=============
  External
=============

Several independent libraries are used by and distributed along with Batajelo.
These libraries were released by their authors under various permissive
free software licences, and you are then allowed to use and distribute them
following their respective licences.

The full licence texts are provided in separated files, and the copyright notices
can be found at the top of each source code file, if provided.


